### Patient Management Service — Body Measurement Endpoints
### Requires: REST Client extension (humao.rest-client)
### Only "admin", "doctor", and "nurse" roles can record measurements.
### All authenticated users can read measurement history.
###
### IMPORTANT: You need a valid patientId before recording measurements.
###            Run patients.http first to create a patient and get its UUID.

@baseUrl   = http://localhost:8001
@token     = PASTE_YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
@staffToken = PASTE_DOCTOR_OR_NURSE_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
@patientId = PASTE_PATIENT_UUID_HERE


# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# POST /api/v1/patients/{patient_id}/measurements  — Record measurement
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 1. Record a full body measurement (height + weight + waist + hip)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/patients/{{patientId}}/measurements
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{staffToken}}

{
  "height_cm": 175.0,
  "weight_kg": 72.5,
  "waist_cm": 85.0,
  "hip_cm": 98.0,
  "measured_at": "2026-07-17T10:00:00Z"
}

###

### 2. Record only weight (partial measurement — at least one field required)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/patients/{{patientId}}/measurements
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{staffToken}}

{
  "weight_kg": 74.2,
  "measured_at": "2026-07-17T14:30:00Z"
}

###

### 3. Record only height and weight — no measured_at (defaults to now)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/patients/{{patientId}}/measurements
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{staffToken}}

{
  "height_cm": 175.0,
  "weight_kg": 71.8
}

###

### 4. Record with waist and hip only (for waist-hip ratio)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/patients/{{patientId}}/measurements
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{staffToken}}

{
  "waist_cm": 83.5,
  "hip_cm": 96.0,
  "measured_at": "2026-07-10T09:00:00Z"
}

###

### 5. Record measurement — expect 404 Not Found (invalid patient UUID)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/patients/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/measurements
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{staffToken}}

{
  "weight_kg": 70.0
}

###

### 6. Record measurement — expect 401 Unauthorized (missing token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/patients/{{patientId}}/measurements
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "weight_kg": 70.0
}

###

### 7. Record measurement — expect 403 Forbidden (receptionist token)
### Login as receptionist user and paste token below
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/patients/{{patientId}}/measurements
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer RECEPTIONIST_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "weight_kg": 70.0
}

###

### 8. Record measurement — expect 422 Unprocessable Entity (no measurement fields)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/patients/{{patientId}}/measurements
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{staffToken}}

{
  "measured_at": "2026-07-17T10:00:00Z"
}


# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# GET /api/v1/patients/{patient_id}/measurements/latest
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

###

### 9. Get latest body measurement for a patient
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/patients/{{patientId}}/measurements/latest
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 10. Get latest measurement — expect 404 Not Found (patient has no measurements)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/patients/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/measurements/latest
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 11. Get latest measurement — expect 401 Unauthorized (missing token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/patients/{{patientId}}/measurements/latest


# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# GET /api/v1/patients/{patient_id}/measurements  — Full history
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

###

### 12. List all measurements — default pagination (limit=20, offset=0)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/patients/{{patientId}}/measurements
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 13. List measurements with custom pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/patients/{{patientId}}/measurements?limit=5&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 14. List measurements — page 2
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/patients/{{patientId}}/measurements?limit=5&offset=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 15. List measurements — expect 404 Not Found (invalid patient UUID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/patients/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/measurements
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 16. List measurements — expect 401 Unauthorized (missing token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/patients/{{patientId}}/measurements
